 - Jennifer Louthan
<!channel>: FWIW: from producer at Mullen: "Site looks great, please be sure to tell the team that we're really happy with what we're seeing."

<@U026AP8CM> from the email you just forwarded: " I did take a look at the site on my iPad and I was a little surprised. We should see the desktop version, and it would be locked in landscape mode. There was even talk of using the gyroscope feature with the beer levels for mobile and iPad. "
I thought we had agreed with the client that iPad would the mobile designs and that we weren't doing anything fancy with the gyroscope.
and we were gonna lock it in portrait..
<@U02613K0X>:  From the same email "Can we still add a new section (such as daily specials) if needed through the CMS?"
i thought we ruled that out several weeks ago
There's a lot of stuff wrong with that email. We can chat and we may need to remind him of stuff we already agreed on. Sorry for any confusion
